OL,3,CConcerns raised over Jersey's
OL,4,Cdwindling tourism industry
OL,6,FFormer government officials and
OL,7,Fhoteliers have voiced their concerns
OL,8,Fover the decline of Jersey's tourism
OL,9,Findustry.
OL,11,FIn the 1970s and 1980s, the island was
OL,12,Fseen as a destination hotspot with a
OL,13,Fbooming visitor economy.
OL,15,FEconomist John Christensen served as
OL,16,Fan advisor for Jersey's government and
OL,17,Fclaims that the State prioritised
OL,18,Ffunding to grow the financial industry
OL,19,Fwhich caused the tourism sector to
OL,20,Fdrop off.
