OL,3,CConcerns raised over Jersey's
OL,4,Cdwindling tourism industry
OL,6,FThe number of hotel beds in Jersey has
OL,7,Fdropped by more than two-thirds since
OL,8,Fthe 1980s, with the latest figure
OL,9,Fstanding at fewer than 10,000 spaces.
OL,11,FAccommodation beds in Jersey across
OL,12,Fthe 21st century:
OL,14,FFormer Jersey politician and Senator
OL,15,FTed Vibert says hotel owners are
OL,16,Fleaving an "unprofitable" tourism
OL,17,Fbusiness, adding that government
OL,18,Finvestment is desperately needed.
