OL,3,CConcerns raised over Jersey's
OL,4,Cdwindling tourism industry
OL,6,FHe explains: "The finance industry is
OL,7,Fsuch an easy industry to run but
OL,8,Fthey've put all their eggs in one
OL,9,Fbasket and totally neglected tourism.
OL,11,F"It has to have government investment
OL,12,Fand infrastructure, every place in the
OL,13,Fworld wants the tourist industry and
OL,14,Fthey're prepared to spend big money,
OL,15,Fwe're just not in the race anymore.
OL,17,F"When you look at how much money has
OL,18,FJersey really invested in tourism and
OL,19,Finfrastructure, we've got nothing."
