OL,3,CConcerns raised over Jersey's
OL,4,Cdwindling tourism industry
OL,6,FGeoff Mayger from the Marina Metro
OL,7,FHotel highlights another issue as he
OL,8,Fbelieves properties like his are "easy
OL,9,Ftargets" for developers to turn into
OL,10,Fhousing, decreasing bed spaces.
OL,12,FHe adds: "This year, we're struggling
OL,13,Feven more and we're just seeing a
OL,14,Fgradual decline.
OL,16,F"Tourism is doing everything it can to
OL,17,Ffight back, but budgets are being cut
OL,18,Fand people have less money to invest.
